import json
p='/Users/louishyman/.openclaw/agents/polly/sessions/19ff066e-1c31-4ae8-af96-92255ca0c056.jsonl'
for i,l in enumerate(open(p),1):
    o=json.loads(l)
    if o.get('type')=='message' and o.get('message',{}).get('role') in ('user','assistant'):
        c=o['message'].get('content')
        if isinstance(c,str):
            txt=c
        else:
            txt=''
            if isinstance(c,list):
                for it in c:
                    if isinstance(it,dict):
                        if 'text' in it: txt += it['text']
                        elif it.get('type')=='input_text': txt += it.get('text','')
                        elif it.get('type')=='output_text': txt += it.get('text','')
        if 'HEARTBEAT_OK' in txt or 'heartbeat' in txt.lower():
            print(i,o['timestamp'],o['message']['role'],txt[:200])
PY

